    <item>
      <title>Pinterest Switches</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/interface/pinterest-switches/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Feb 2012 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/interface/pinterest-switches/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Sure you can use a checkbox to enter binary values in a form, but Pinterest goes the hi-fi route and instead uses sexy switches, a la iOS controls, in their email settings form.&lt;/p&gt;

